trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when an error condition occurs during the opening, accessing, or using of a [PrintDialog](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Undantag som utlöses när ett fel inträffar under den inledande åtkomst till, eller om hur du använder en [PrintDialog](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"></xref> class that provides a specific error condition in a <xref:System.String> .
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"> </xref> klass som innehåller en specifik feltillstånd i <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that describes the error condition.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"></xref> class that provides specific <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> and <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"> </xref> klass som innehåller specifika <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> och <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: The data that is required to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: De data som krävs för att serialisera eller deserialisering av objekt.

trans-unit.source: The context, including source and destination, of the serialized stream.
trans-unit.target: Kontexten, inklusive källa och mål för den serialiserade dataströmmen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"></xref> class that provides a specific error condition, including its underlying cause.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"> </xref> klass som innehåller ett specifikt fel villkor, inklusive den bakomliggande orsaken.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.String> that describes the error condition.
The underlying error condition that caused the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det underliggande felet villkor som orsakade det <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.PrintDialogException"> </xref>.
